Source: delphix-meta
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Delphix Engineering <eng@delphix.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), germinate (>= 1.18)
Standards-Version: 4.1.2

Package: delphix-foundation
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Description: Foundation for Delphix Appliance
 This package depends on all of the packages that provide the foundation for
 the Delphix Appliance. This set of packages provide the necessary tools to
 run a root filesystem on OpenZFS, and provide various utilities to facilliate
 efficient debugging of common problems.
